Q.  What is Kadane Algorithim?
A.  Kadane’s algorithm focuses on whether to continue the current subarray or start a new subarray.
    | Choice             | Meaning                             |
    | ------------------ | ----------------------------------- |
    | Start new subarray | Take current element only           |
    | Continue subarray  | Add current element to previous sum |
    currentSum = Math.max(nums[i], currentSum + nums[i]);
